Package: gnutls-wolfssl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libwolfssl
Section: libs
Description: GnuTLS built against system wolfSSL
 GnuTLS 3.x rebuilt to use the system-provided wolfSSL as its
 cryptographic backend. Installs under /opt/gnutls by default,
 if GNUTLS_INSTALL is not provided.

Package: wolfssl-gnutls-wrapper
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gnutls-wolfssl, libwolfssl
Section: libs
Description: Runtime shim between GnuTLS and wolfSSL
 Thin provider / wrapper that allows applications to load the
 wolfSSL-backed GnuTLS seamlessly. Installs under /opt/wolfssl-gnutls-wrapper,
 if PROVIDER_PATH is not provided.
